import React from 'react' const Rating = ({ value, text }) => { return (
{/* STAR 1 */} = 1 ? 'fas fa-star' : value >= 0.5 ? 'fas fa-star-half-alt' : 'far fa-star' } > {/* STAR 2 */} = 2 ? 'fas fa-star' : value >= 1.5 ? 'fas fa-star-half-alt' : 'far fa-star' } > {/* STAR 3 */} = 3 ? 'fas fa-star' : value >= 2.5 ? 'fas fa-star-half-alt' : 'far fa-star' } > {/* STAR 4 */} = 4 ? 'fas fa-star' : value >= 3.5 ? 'fas fa-star-half-alt' : 'far fa-star' } > = 5 ? 'fas fa-star' : value >= 4.5 ? 'fas fa-star-half-alt' : 'far fa-star' } > {text && text}
) } export default Rating
